latestIgtvVideos.title: #ParkedCarsCanRunFamilies
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Sad to see the watchman of my building facing the pandemic and performing his risky job. There are several people coming in back to their homes and he had to be in contact with all. 
Then, I came across this short video by @ackoinsurance featuring my favourites #SaurabhShukla #AliFazal #ManjotSingh . It taught me how not driving the vehicle this lockdown saved my money and this money can be used for the less-remembered heroes in my life.

I helped him with masks, sanitizers and other necessities. 
I urge everyone to financially help these people because #ParkedCarsCanRunFamilies

latestPosts.caption:
Finally, a TEDx speaker!🫶🏻@ted @tedx_official 
Firsts are always so special 🙏🏻
One of my biggest manifestations—accomplished.
When I look back, this journey was far from easy. It tested me, challenged me, but shaped me in ways I never imagined. And 9 years later, the little girl in me is proud, SO PROUD 🥹🧿
This moment is a reminder that dreams do come true.
I’m honestly short of words, this feeling is surreal.
Thank you to everyone who believed in me, stood by me, and cheered for me, and to my family for always being there throughout 🫶🏻🙏🏻
We did it 🙌🏻 😭😭

Grateful to the entire team of @tedxvitpune but special thanks to @tiluckdave @aryaa_sharma_05 @divysayys @its_divyaasnani @shreeshail_chitpur @riteshjadhav_ 🫶🏻❤️❤️
Wouldn’t have been possible without you guys! I still can’t believe we pulled this off in less than 5 days 🙏🏻🙌🏻

latestPosts.caption:
As a little girl, she’d walk past hoardings and look up —
Not just at the celebrities on them,
But at the possibility of being seen. Of being someone. 🌇✨

She never imagined that one day, she’d be the one on them.

Naina R Ahluwalia’s journey didn’t begin with glam or spotlight.
It began in a quiet room —
📖 writing thoughtful blogs,
📷 capturing light through her lens,
and 💭 dreaming big without needing to be loud.

She didn’t follow trends — she followed what felt true. 🌿

Over the years, she evolved with the digital space:
📸 From stills to Reels
✍️ From long captions to bite-sized stories
But her anchor stayed the same: authenticity.

💚 She built a brand not on numbers, but on connection
🌍 Her first international brand trip wasn’t just a milestone — it was a full-circle moment
🎤 She stood on a TEDx stage, not to talk about virality, but vulnerability.

Even now, success looks like this:
🌤 Morning walks
👨‍👩‍👧‍👦 Time with family
🌳 Nature
📝 Storytelling
Softness that still makes waves.

And when asked if she’d ever trade lives with someone for a day?
She smiled and said no.
Because this life — slow, soulful, intentional — is hers.
And she’s writing it just the way she always dreamed. ✨🕊️

Swipe through to read the story of a creator who didn’t just grow —
She glowed from within.

👉 Full interview live now on @eatmynews
